results.name: Orbit size of n in permutation A163355.
comment: Will all terms of A003586 eventually appear?
link: A. Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..262143
program: (Scheme:) (define (A163890 n) (let loop ((i 1) (nn (A163355 n))) (cond ((= nn n) i) (else (loop (1+ i) (A163355 nn))))))
